  "A bakery makes cakes and pies. Each cake needs 3 cups of flour and each pie needs 2 cups. They used 24 cups for 10 items. How many cakes were made?": "",
  "c + p = 10 and 3c + 2p = 24. Substituting p = 10 - c: 3c + 20 - 2c = 24, c = 4.": "",
